OL,6,FA man has admitted to stabbing his
OL,7,Fwife to death at their home in
OL,8,FWolverhampton.
OL,10,FRajveer Mahey was charged with the
OL,11,Fmurder of 46-year-old Kamaljeet Mahey
OL,12,Fon Park Meadow Avenue, Bilston in
OL,13,FDecember 2023.
OL,15,FThe 50-year-old pleaded guilty to her
OL,16,Fmurder at Wolverhampton Crown Court on
OL,17,FMonday 18 March.
OL,19,FHe has been remanded in custody for
OL,20,Fsentencing on 19 April.
