OL,6,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,7,FInspector Jim Mahon, said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with Mrs Mahey's
OL,9,Fchildren and family who continue to
OL,10,Fgrieve for their much loved mother and
OL,11,Floved one.
OL,13,F"This case is a tragic case that has
OL,14,Fleft a family without a mother and a
OL,15,Ffather.
OL,17,F"We believe the murder may have been
OL,18,Fdriven by unsubstantiated jealousy but
OL,19,Fthe true motive may never be known."
